{"tid":1217871,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"英國大學開始share逃犯條例！","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T22:15:36.000Z","uid":67295,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8cd07cf9d3643443207e9467ade1717e3b30b4","tid":1217871,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"好啦其實係我黎 不過見好多同學都想出分力 甚至到遊行有外國人支持我地<br />\n希望大家可以post係自己大學個page度 即使上唔到街 都令更多人留意同簽署<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtcuXFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtcuXFX.png&h=ea4f9b36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2q3aG7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2q3aG7F.png&h=2ed04e7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bf524c0126470fe44367045318c2bb04dec0a88","tid":1217871,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"段文 啲link我都係reddit copy<br />\n<br />\n#noextraditionbill<br />\n<br />\nRegarding the protest in Hong Kong, it is still happening. Reading in the Legislative Council is scheduled every weekday until 24th June. I believe Hong Kong needs help from everywhere in the world. And I would be sincerely pleased if all of you could sign these petitions.<br />\n<br />\nThere are six white house petition right now.<br />\n<br />\n有人整理左全部屬於簽名既weblinks，希望大家share出去出一份力 thanks 🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n1⃣Reject Immigration or Non-Immigration Visas of Hong Kong Government Officials Violating Human Rights<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/reject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Freject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e6b89352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/reject-immigration-or-non-immigration-visas-hong-kong-government-officials-violating-human-rights</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣Revoke the U.S. Citizenship and Visas of the Hong Kong and China Officials who are in Support of the Extradition Bill<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=3ae3630f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill</a><br />\n<br />\n3⃣Extradition Law Amendment in Hong Kong &mdash; Threat to Personal Safety and Freedom<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=9de99cc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n4⃣全球聯署【反送中 民意不可欺 為香港企硬】Global Signing: Against Extradition to China<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E